<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ticket Status Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #008000;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #008000;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #008000;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Ticket Status Update</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p><strong>Ticket Number:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%=  @ticket_number %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Date Created:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%=  @ticket_created_at %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Issue Summary:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%=  @issue_description %></span></p>

            <p>Hello <strong> <%= @customer_email %></strong>,</p>
            <p>
                Our support team is currently reviewing your issue and will contact you as soon as possible with an update.
                 In the meantime, you can track the progress of your ticket by logging into your account 
                 using the button below. <span class="highlight">when you are logged in, click on the "Support Ticket" tab</span>
            </p>
            <p>
                We will keep you informed via email of any updates or changes to your ticket status. 
                If you have any further questions or additional information to provide, please feel free to contact us. Thank you for your patience!
            </p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href=<%=@tracking_url %> class="button">Track Your Ticket</a>
            </div>
            <p>Best regards,</p> 
            <p>The <span class="highlight"><%= @company_name %></span> Team</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                Contact us at: <a href="mailto:<%= @customer_support_email %>"><%= @customer_support_email %></a> 
                | <a href="tel:<%= @customer_support_phone_number %>"><%= @customer_support_phone_number %></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %>  <%=@company_name %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
